Currently the Requested Participant field is a Multi User Picker. We have some use cases where a reporter would like to add their JIRA group/team as a participant to the reported issue rather than adding each member of their team individually. 

A simplified solution would be to allow for groups to be selected with the UI and upon submitting the users in the group get added to the Requested Participant field individually.

