Just a potentially nice feature, it would be nice if you could have form sections on Jira Service Desk forms that are based of the create screen configuration for the issue type you've selected.

For example on the the create screen configuration if you leave all fields on the main tab then the form would be as it is now, but if you configure fields on different tabs it would make form sections using the tab name and position left to right on the create screen configuration.

For the time being we have to put section indicators in the helptext of the fields on the form.

