We really need to be able to see who was the last responder in a ticket.  Our administrator filters all tickets and notifies our users that we've received their response and that we are transferring the ticket to a developer.  The developer then looks at their list and works on any ticket that is awaiting support.  Unfortunately the comment left by our admin causes the status to change to Waiting on Customer. As a result we're having to go through all tickets regardless of status to see if a response is required.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
