*Problem Statement*

When using reports for JIRA Service Desk, users can only choose predetermined time intervals. This feature should allow more flexibility, such as allowing customer to specify different time intervals, and choose older dates as well.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Service Desk Cloud*. Using *JIRA Service Desk Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSDSERVER-4047].
