We are getting consistent requests to see the last updated time in various Queue's in our JSD implementation.  The Time stamp will help an agent know which tickets are lagging in response for the day and help them keep on top of the status.  We looked at options for using SLA clocks and the likes but none of these options are getting us where we'd like to be.

