We generate email notifications outside JSD from a P2 plugin and want to replicate/integrate with the Customer Satisfaction feedback feature of JSD notifications from our notification.  From what I can see there is an internal component {RequestFeedbackTokenInternalManager}} that would need exposing, as it not only generates the specific tokens but stores them for association/validation on the inbound URL.

In order to integrate with this feature, we'd need the RequestFeedbackTokenInternalManager published.

